            "id": 6405676,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 華懋(5292)大跌7.64%，報211.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華懋(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:5292:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5292\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5292-TW</a>)02日12:22股價下跌17.5元，報211.5元，跌幅7.64%，成交408張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華懋(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:5292:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5292\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5292-TW</a>)所屬產業為綠能環保，主要業務為VOC設備工程。工業用除濕機。VOC設備維修保養。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.09%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.79%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+657 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+653 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+5 張</li> <li>融資增減：+2 張</li> <li>融券增減：+2 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
